code: @Override public void onComplete(Object response) {     exchange.getOut().setHeaders(exchange.getIn().getHeaders()).     if (response == null) {         exchange.getOut().setBody(response).     } else {         exchange.getOut().setBody(response, response.getClass()).     }     callback.done(false). }
@Override public void onError(Exception exception) {     exchange.setException(exception).     callback.done(false). }
